{"tid":274541,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關physics ce past paper mc electricity既問題","createTime":"2017-06-07T11:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T13:08:56.000Z","uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6256af52fce8302ca901c54b92c784b5fdb3dd","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"小弟對electricity稍為不佳<br />\n跪求各高手相助<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/265hr7bc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F265hr7bc&h=2e4cb610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問為何Q所得數據並非-1.5V?<br />\n<br />\n據我所知<br />\n假如P量度到1.5V<br />\n則Q應該量度到-1.5V<br />\n因為假設整條電路沒有任何能量損耗<br />\n電位差應為0<br />\n正電荷前去低電勢的Q點<br />\n則Q點應度到-1.5V<br />\n<br />\n小弟對電位/電勢(electric potential)既概念可能混淆了<br />\n有錯請隨便責備<br />\n亦懇求各高手有隙解釋一下我既錯處"},{"pid":"3f7dab5e15e6aad8b242c1e276a6f2c11bfa781d","tid":274541,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:19:42.000Z","msg":"Ask your miss Lai shan yee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da91c257ba15bc6992cd577990092f7bd1f9df8e","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ask your miss Lai shan yee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恐怕不能<br />\n明日並無其課堂"},{"pid":"b7c2fa95881c5a77baa6daa63ddf29ec5178dde6","tid":274541,"uid":36964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"miss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac9558dda35ae654a32267c553a82975234bac7","tid":274541,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ask your miss Lai shan yee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恐怕不能<br />\n明日並無其課堂</blockquote><br />\n聽日無你唔識問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a298289c883876838d8aac0a6fcdc5bba8ffd8ac","tid":274541,"uid":58489,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"A<br />\n唔係complete circuit冇電通過"},{"pid":"8ba42cac6b98ec19896dc3f6fcbfc56eb386f411","tid":274541,"uid":45740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"v=ir<br />\n<br />\n佢一定冇 current <br />\nv=(0)r<br />\nv=0<br />\n<br />\n你個諗法係直接唔理cell嘅definition <br />\n好難解到你明喎"},{"pid":"7276762abd9ed49a27731b8663d089e569f815e5","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A<br />\n唔係complete circuit冇電通過</blockquote><br />\n答案為C<br />\n但感謝你的相助<br />\n可留下golden account許我賜酒<br />\n本人習慣賜酒俾善人<br />\n<br />\n若冇，即場敬你一杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d0b19e6347b8cfcf4070242c8505fbc0b09939","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>v=ir<br />\n<br />\n佢一定冇 current <br />\nv=(0)r<br />\nv=0<br />\n<br />\n你個諗法係直接唔理cell嘅definition <br />\n好難解到你明喎</blockquote><br />\n既然有口難言<br />\n無謂麻煩巴打<br />\n可以退下火線了<br />\n賜你一杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b84957f3460d5c7bef82db47dfb447128adbfa4","tid":274541,"uid":101044,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:36:09.000Z","msg":"因為open circuit嗰陣個current會過哂去個voltmeter, 而因為voltmeter resistance極大，會食哂個current啲voltage，好似係"},{"pid":"09bb50bb053ef3de39f6bc6fbf06ea1955b1b64e","tid":274541,"uid":101044,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟對electricity稍為不佳<br />\n跪求各高手相助<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/265hr7bc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F265hr7bc&h=2e4cb610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問為何Q所得數據並非-1.5V?<br />\n<br />\n據我所知<br />\n假如P量度到1.5V<br />\n則Q應該量度到-1.5V<br />\n因為假設整條電路沒有任何能量損耗<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n一定會有能量損耗"},{"pid":"7965df3978d14b0619a22638b9a20387cd9994c8","tid":274541,"uid":7032,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟對electricity稍為不佳<br />\n跪求各高手相助<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/265hr7bc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F265hr7bc&h=2e4cb610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問為何Q所得數據並非-1.5V?<br />\n<br />\n據我所知<br />\n假如P量度到1.5V<br />\n則Q應該量度到-1.5V<br />\n因為假設整條電路沒有任何能量損耗<br />\n電位差應為0<br />\n正電荷前去低電勢的Q點<br />\n則Q點應度到-1.5V<br />\n<br />\n小弟對電位/電勢(electric potential)既概念可能混淆了<br />\n有錯請隨便責備<br />\n亦懇求各高手有隙解釋一下我既錯處</blockquote><br />\n唔明你講啲咩，但應該唔會有負voltage，1.5v係因為p嗰個位open circuit咗，所以所有voltage差 會喺p位走曬，所以係1.5v，而因為voltage已經走曬，又唔係complete circuit，所以q係0"},{"pid":"848088ddd5300a358127da4bad61d61f6deb8364","tid":274541,"uid":73757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"voltmeter resistance大過電泡好多，咁其實可以唔洗理個電泡，咁就知道點解答案係c"},{"pid":"d6ae8f2c3d2d00c04e5dca91bc8f24c250e4a54f","tid":274541,"uid":82452,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:45:13.000Z","msg":"簡單d諗 <br />\n一個 voltmeter係 assume無限 resistance <br />\n係 V(total ) =\tIR(voltmeter)  + IR(light bulb)  <br />\n咁你覺得 light bulb個R有冇得同 voltmeter鬥  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外有人話 + 1.5 同 - 1.5 係有個missing 位 <br />\n計少左 電池 <br />\n<br />\nv (電池)  = -1.5 <br />\nv (voltmeter P)  = +1.5  <br />\n咁咪已經 0 左 <br />\n仲邊有voltage比個light bulb"},{"pid":"4edd7ea67f8f49d116ee311968d81f45aee9b4cf","tid":274541,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A<br />\n唔係complete circuit冇電通過</blockquote><br />\n邊個話無電過就無voltage<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab1a284a788e259fb137bc25c3400fbe7df7e9e","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"感謝各位相助<br />\n我已經大概知道咩事了<br />\n所以話連登仔既教學真係第一<br />\n用風趣幽默既方式教功課<br />\n教學效率真係高<br />\n真係冇得頂"},{"pid":"794abe75ebc8ae31d8b38c755f981caccb1300a5","tid":274541,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"Voltmeter 讀嘅係電勢<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span><br />\n因為冇電流經過燈泡，所以燈泡前後電勢冇分別<br />\n咁樣會唔會易明啲"},{"pid":"e52d121df151ad2fa3f4f484187608b7459829c9","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Voltmeter 讀嘅係電勢<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span><br />\n因為冇電流經過燈泡，所以燈泡前後電勢冇分別<br />\n咁樣會唔會易明啲</blockquote><br />\n那麼P亦冇current經過<br />\n然而其電勢都係1.5V<br />\nopen circuit某點的電勢不一定係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01032ff38c479b219eea3e82e621a4c3539620ff","tid":274541,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Voltmeter 讀嘅係電勢<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span><br />\n因為冇電流經過燈泡，所以燈泡前後電勢冇分別<br />\n咁樣會唔會易明啲</blockquote><br />\n那麼P亦冇current經過<br />\n然而其電勢都係1.5V<br />\nopen circuit某點的電勢不一定係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先你要搞清楚電勢同電勢差嘅分別先<br />\nvoltmeter P 連住嗰兩點之間有個cell，導致兩點之間electric potential有分別，但係叧一個voltmeter就冇"},{"pid":"8236ffa09fdc5893bdb3424f8a7324123b3c5a1a","tid":274541,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"電流當做人流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nVoltage 姐係有幾多錢，你將d錢洗哂去個voltmeter 到，咪1.5，咁去到下一個voltmeter ，你都無哂錢，咪0<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我跟ken chan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016031bf6cd6e7ff4dbc714551b32250039be369","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Voltmeter 讀嘅係電勢<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span><br />\n因為冇電流經過燈泡，所以燈泡前後電勢冇分別<br />\n咁樣會唔會易明啲</blockquote><br />\n那麼P亦冇current經過<br />\n然而其電勢都係1.5V<br />\nopen circuit某點的電勢不一定係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先你要搞清楚電勢同電勢差嘅分別先<br />\nvoltmeter P 連住嗰兩點之間有個cell，導致兩點之間electric potential有分別，但係叧一個voltmeter就冇</blockquote><br />\n電勢差既定義係兩點之間，"},{"pid":"f756bdd9378062240f882f15109ef9ed3d2fab19","tid":274541,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Voltmeter 讀嘅係電勢<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span><br />\n因為冇電流經過燈泡，所以燈泡前後電勢冇分別<br />\n咁樣會唔會易明啲</blockquote><br />\n那麼P亦冇current經過<br />\n然而其電勢都係1.5V<br />\nopen circuit某點的電勢不一定係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先你要搞清楚電勢同電勢差嘅分別先<br />\nvoltmeter P 連住嗰兩點之間有個cell，導致兩點之間electric potential有分別，但係叧一個voltmeter就冇</blockquote><br />\n電勢差既定義係兩點之間，</blockquote><br />\n電勢差既定義唔係兩點之間，個charge移動作既功既相差咩?<br />\n既然如此<br />\n則Q點連住cell個點應有電勢<br />\n而連住另一邊個點則係0電勢<br />\n換言之兩點有電勢差<br />\nvoltmeter 應該度到野<br />\n可能我Concept錯晒<br />\n有錯請屌"},{"pid":"e1ac06232b1e9e378aca906a367bf1393c780f0d","tid":274541,"uid":119433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Voltmeter 讀嘅係電勢<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span><br />\n因為冇電流經過燈泡，所以燈泡前後電勢冇分別<br />\n咁樣會唔會易明啲</blockquote><br />\n那麼P亦冇current經過<br />\n然而其電勢都係1.5V<br />\nopen circuit某點的電勢不一定係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先你要搞清楚電勢同電勢差嘅分別先<br />\nvoltmeter P 連住嗰兩點之間有個cell，導致兩點之間electric potential有分別，但係叧一個voltmeter就冇</blockquote><br />\n電勢差既定義係兩點之間，</blockquote><br />\n電勢差既定義唔係兩點之間，個charge移動作既功既相差咩?<br />\n既然如此<br />\n則Q點連住cell個點應有電勢<br />\n而連住另一邊個點則係0電勢<br />\n換言之兩點有電勢差<br />\nvoltmeter 應該度到野<br />\n可能我Concept錯晒<br />\n有錯請屌</blockquote><br />\nQ點連住cell果點係0電勢<br />\n另一邊電勢又係0<br />\n電勢差=0"},{"pid":"458c91cfc01187d4850433f7ee8a39a8ca1563ad","tid":274541,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Voltmeter 讀嘅係電勢<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span><br />\n因為冇電流經過燈泡，所以燈泡前後電勢冇分別<br />\n咁樣會唔會易明啲</blockquote><br />\n那麼P亦冇current經過<br />\n然而其電勢都係1.5V<br />\nopen circuit某點的電勢不一定係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先你要搞清楚電勢同電勢差嘅分別先<br />\nvoltmeter P 連住嗰兩點之間有個cell，導致兩點之間electric potential有分別，但係叧一個voltmeter就冇</blockquote><br />\n電勢差既定義係兩點之間，</blockquote><br />\n電勢差既定義唔係兩點之間，個charge移動作既功既相差咩?<br />\n既然如此<br />\n則Q點連住cell個點應有電勢<br />\n而連住另一邊個點則係0電勢<br />\n換言之兩點有電勢差<br />\nvoltmeter 應該度到野<br />\n可能我Concept錯晒<br />\n有錯請屌</blockquote><br />\n你嘅理解啱但係後面嘅推論唔啱<br />\n<br />\n電勢其實好似高度咁<br />\n電勢高嘅地方，charge會有較高嘅電勢能<br />\n好似一個波喺高嘅地方會有高啲嘅位勢能<br />\n<br />\n當charge經過電阻，就會損耗勢能，變成其他能量，例如經過燈泡會變熱、發光<br />\n好似一個波向下跌，勢能變咗做動能咁<br />\n<br />\n當電流為零時，燈泡係唔會損耗任何能量，因為根本冇著<br />\n所以燈泡前後電勢係冇分別"},{"pid":"40c07c2c4ce6aac736fc03c55441156bc8b9b429","tid":274541,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"另外如果一個circuit冇接地嘅話，一般係唔應該assume任何一點係0電勢<br />\n唔影響理解呢題，只係concept問題"}]}